description:
Summer vacation is here! Visit My Town Paradise Island, and explore the Tropical Beach!

Take a swimming suit and play fun beach games on your vacation! Go swimming, surfing or have a nice picnic party on the beach! Play and discover many gifts exploring our Paradise Island! My Town has fun family games for kids!

What’s more beautiful than playing summer games in the sand, swimming in the sea or having a picnic with your friends? Enjoy My Town Summer Vacation games for kids and have a lot of fun!

EXPLORE MY TOWN PARADISE ISLAND

Summer Vacation started! Dive into a mermaid's underworld, play and discover a paradise Island's hidden treasure, go surfing, swim, and enjoy in many beach games!

Dad! You just caught old boots! What? Yes, you can go fishing and try to have a good catch so you can have something nice for the picnic lunch! Visit our paradise island and enjoy playing My Town fun family games for kids! My Town Summer Beach Picnic is for all who like to play camping games with many fun vacation activities!

CREATE A TROPICAL BEACH PARTY

Create a tropical beach party on this paradise island! Call your friends and let the music play! Start the best beach party ever! Many summer vacation games that you can play: swimming games, surfing, table tennis, snorkeling and more! Our paradise island has many fun games for girls and boys!

SET UP A CAMP – START A PICNIC

Pick your favorite food: ice cream or a sandwich for your picnic and enjoy camping games! Make sure there is enough lemonade for all picnic guests! Enjoy My Town Beach game. Check why My Town has the best fun games for girls and boys!

MY TOWN BEACH FEATURES:
Your summer vacation started!
Play and discover 5 NEW locations during your vacation on Paradise Island:
-      Beach bar 
-      Paradise Island Treehouse
-      Tropical Beach and more
Enjoy swimming games, surfing and snorkeling
Explore the Sea underworld!
Enjoy fishing, camping, picnic and more beach games!
NEW characters: Surfer, Scuba diver, and more!
Pick your favorite summer outfit 
Create Tropical Beach Party!
Like surfing? Designing your surfboard and ride the wave
Build the most beautiful sandcastle

ENJOY SUMMER VACATION GAMES

My Town Beach game allows kids to enjoy summer games and relax! 
Our fun games for girls and boys will improve kids' creativity and imagination! There are no surfing, snorkeling, or swimming game competitions! Only fun! My Town Beach Paradise Island is full of fun family games for kids!
Visit a shopping store during your summer vacation and choose the perfect outfit for your picnic, camping, or Beach Party!

LEARN WHILE PLAYING

Kids will learn much about the environment while playing our My Town Beach Summer Picnic game! The more garbage you pick up from the beach, the more fish you will see underwater! By playing My Town Summer games like beach games, camping, or swimming games, kids will improve their memory and creativity!

RECOMMENDED AGE GROUP
Kids 4-12. The game is safe even when parents are out of the room. 

ABOUT MY TOWN

The My Town Home Games studio designs digital dollhouse games that promote creativity and open role-play for all kids. The company has offices in Israel, Spain, Romania and the Philippines. For more information, visit www.my-town.com
